If you use SkyPy for work/research presented in a publication (whether
directly, or as a dependency to another package) please cite both:

  - The SkyPy Concept DoI: https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3755531

and:

  - The Version DoI for the exact version of SkyPy you have used.
    e.g. for v0.1: https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3755532

We also recommend and encourage the following acknowledgement:

  This research made use of SkyPy, a Python package for forward modeling
  astronomical surveys (http://skypy.info).
